    One of the first talents a Summoner learns is how to call forth
raw Elements and combine them for various effects. Mainly for combat,
these spells aid you in defeating your foes; note that you need time
to prepare for and recover from each spell.

Combination spells available:
  - ice            - blaze
  - mud            - magma
  - cyclone        - bolt
  - smoke

For more information on any above spell, type: help <spell>
